race.comment: OLNEY (10) is fitter for two runs in and put the writing on the wall latest when just missed over 1800m. Fitter and extra trip a plus. Only run here at home at this trip was unplaced but ran fifth in much richer company. Will roll forward and expected to take beating tonight. FIERY DEAL (11) hasn't been far away recently and is at top. Tricky gate but has upside and worth following up. CLINGER (3) was safely held fresh but then improved out of sight when up to 1500m. First try at this trip but drops in weight and will give a sight on speed. VERIFIER (7) has race dover 2100m at last two and both in richer company. Looks ideally placed this level and won't get a better chance to find some form.
